docs.name: Detailed Data on the Distribution of World Output, AD1-2012
docs.description: Units: billion of euros 2012, PPP. Source: Author's calculations based on Angus Maddison's historical series, 'Historical statistics of the world economy 1-2008' (February 2010) and official series from the UN and the World Bank for the period 1990-2012 (Octobre 2012). Russia was included in Europe and former Central Asian Republiques and Oceania in Asia. All the details are given in the excel file: MaddisonWorldGDPSeries1to2008.xls, sheet 'CorrectedSummaryTables'. The link to this file was broken on 2-8-2013.  Maddison data is on Quandl.com
